OL,5,G2100 A&E After Dark
OL,6,     FIn Newham, a boy, 19, lies with a
OL,7,     Fpotentially broken neck after a
OL,8,     Fjudo match - any movement could
OL,9,     Fworsen his injury. Meanwhile,
OL,10,     Fdoctors fight to save a patient
OL,11,     Fwith a collapsed lung.
OL,12,G2200 Ambulance: Code Red
OL,13,     FA workplace accident ends with a
OL,14,     Fman pushed through a sheet of
OL,15,     Fglass, and responders have to
OL,16,     Fhandle the cuts; a stabbing victim
OL,17,     Frisks bleeding out on the street.
