OL,5,G2300 Skin A&E
OL,6,     FDr Toby treats one of the largest
OL,7,     Flipomas the clinic has seen; Dr
OL,8,     FNatalia deals with a supersized
OL,9,     Fwarty lesion; Dr Emma sorts out a
OL,10,     Fcyst that patient Barry's wife has
OL,11,     Fenjoyed squeezing.
OL,12,G0000 Plastic Surgery Nightmares
OL,13,     FIn this episode, we tell the
OL,14,     Fshocking story of how one woman,
OL,15,     FMarie ended up being rushed into
OL,16,     Fhospital when surgery to remove
OL,17,     Fexcess skin left her with life
OL,18,     Fthreatening sepsis.
